OL,3,CXabi Alonso appointed Chelsea manager
OL,4,Con four-year deal
OL,6,FXabi Alonso's appointment as Chelsea
OL,7,Fmanager has been confirmed on a four-
OL,8,Fyear deal.
OL,10,FThe former Real Madrid boss will take
OL,11,Fcharge of the Blues from July 1 in
OL,12,Fwhat is his first managerial role in
OL,13,Fthe Premier League.
OL,15,FCallum McFarlane has been in interim
OL,16,Fcharge since the sacking of Liam
OL,17,FRosenior last month and was on the
OL,18,Ftouchline for Chelsea's FA Cup final
OL,19,Floss to Manchester City on Saturday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
