OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779019867
OL,3,CXabi Alonso appointed Chelsea manager
OL,4,Con four-year deal
OL,6,FIt emerged soon after the 1-0 defeat
OL,7,Fthat Chelsea had reached an agreement
OL,8,Fin principle with Alonso, who becomes
OL,9,Fthe latest appointment under BlueCo's
OL,10,Fownership.
OL,12,FThe 44-year-old Spaniard said on
OL,13,Fchelseafc.com: "Chelsea is one of the
OL,14,Fbiggest clubs in world football and it
OL,15,Ffills me with immense pride to become
OL,16,Fmanager of this great club.
OL,26,@uD@POU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
