OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779019867
OL,3,CXabi Alonso appointed Chelsea manager
OL,4,Con four-year deal
OL,6,F"From my conversations with the
OL,7,Fownership group and sporting
OL,8,Fleadership, it is clear we share the
OL,9,Fsame ambition. We want to build a team
OL,10,Fcapable of competing consistently at
OL,11,Fthe highest level and fighting for
OL,12,Ftrophies.
OL,14,F"There is great talent in the squad
OL,15,Fand huge potential at this football
OL,16,Fclub and it will be my great honour to
OL,17,Flead it. Now the focus is on hard
OL,18,Fwork, building the right culture and
OL,19,Fwinning trophies."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
