OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779019867
OL,3,CXabi Alonso appointed Chelsea manager
OL,4,Con four-year deal
OL,6,FChelsea began the season with Enzo
OL,7,FMaresca in charge, but he departed in
OL,8,FJanuary following tension with the
OL,9,Fclub's hierarchy, who then turned to
OL,10,FRosenior, only to sack him after just
OL,11,Fthree months.
OL,13,FA group of Chelsea supporters staged a
OL,14,Fprotest outside Wembley on Saturday to
OL,15,Fvoice their dissatisfaction with the
OL,16,Fowners.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
