PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779019867
OL,3,CXabi Alonso appointed Chelsea manager
OL,4,Con four-year deal
OL,6,FBlueCo will hope that former Liverpool
OL,7,Fand Real Madrid midfielder Alonso
OL,8,Fproves to be the man to bring
OL,9,Fstability to the club, having made a
OL,10,Fhugely impressive start to his
OL,11,Fmanagerial career by guiding Bayer
OL,12,FLeverkusen to an unbeaten season in
OL,13,Fwinning the Bundesliga.
OL,15,FThat earned him a chance to take
OL,16,Fcharge at the Bernabeu, but it did not
OL,17,Fprove to be nearly as happy an
OL,18,Fexperience, with Alonso departing in
OL,19,FJanuary after only seven months.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
