CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779019867
OL,3,CXabi Alonso appointed Chelsea manager
OL,4,Con four-year deal
OL,6,FIn announcing Alonso's appointment,
OL,7,FChelsea described him as "one of the
OL,8,Fmost respected figures in the modern
OL,9,Fgame".
OL,11,F"His appointment reflects the club's
OL,12,Fbelief in his broad set of
OL,13,Fexperiences, coaching quality and game
OL,14,Fmodel, leadership attributes,
OL,15,Fcharacter and integrity, which were
OL,16,Fkey to the decision to ask him to help
OL,17,Flead the next phase of Chelsea's
OL,18,Fjourney," read a statement.
