OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1779019867
OL,3,CXabi Alonso appointed Chelsea manager
OL,4,Con four-year deal
OL,6,F"Chelsea Football Club looks forward
OL,7,Fwith confidence to the next phase in
OL,8,Fcollaboration with Xabi, united in the
OL,9,Fdetermination to bring success to
OL,10,FStamford Bridge, a hallmark of the
OL,11,Fclub's history and future."
